plot: On her birthday, a nostalgic Jubilee is forced to relive the X-Men's greatest adventures when an entertainment system transports her into a 16-bit video game.

In Motendo, Jubilee looks to celebrate her 18th birthday and is trapped in a video game with Roberto. In the second pat, Lifedeath, the man who helped designed the machine that stripped Storm of her powers take her in and tries to reverse her power loss.—Gislef
